title: High-power PS4 model something Sony might consider exec says hypothetically
text:
'High-power' PS4 model something Sony might consider, exec says hypothetically 
Cnet Saturday 24th October, 2015 
"world's most powerful console." That's according to Sony Computer Entertainment senior vice president Masayasu Ito, who was asked for his thoughts in a new interview about offering a new PS4 model with better performance sometime down the road....
